{"@context":"http://iiif.io/api/presentation/3/context.json","id":"https://digbmc.github.io/pta-manifests/phan/phan-14724/manifest.json","type":"Manifest","label":{"none":["PHAN-14724"]},"metadata":[{"label":{"none":["Timestamp"]},"value":{"none":["1:47:24"]}},{"label":{"none":["Film"]},"value":{"none":["Phantom Thread"]}},{"label":{"none":["Distance"]},"value":{"none":["medium shot"]}},{"label":{"none":["Angle"]},"value":{"none":["eye-level"]}},{"label":{"none":["Location"]},"value":{"none":["interior"]}},{"label":{"none":["Movement"]},"value":{"none":["handheld, fixed"]}},{"label":{"none":["Composition"]},"value":{"none":["dirty single"]}}],"summary":{"none":["Man sits with head in his hand, looking down"]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14724/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"homepage":[{"id":"PHAN-14724","type":"Text","format":"text/html","label":{"none":["Object homepage"]}}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14724/canvas/1","type":"Canvas","height":1080,"width":1920,"label":{"none":["PHAN-14724"]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14724/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14724/canvas/1/annopage-1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14724/canvas/1/annopage-1/anno-1","type":"Annotation","motivation":"painting","target":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14724/canvas/1","body":{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14724/tiles/full/1920,1080/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":1080,"width":1920,"service":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14724/tiles","type":"ImageService3","profile":"http://iiif.io/api/image/3/level0.json"}]}}]}],"annotations":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14724/canvas/1/page/p1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14724/canvas/1/dff3a781-0a13-4faa-89a1-f0a3baa18605","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-07-01T19:06:02.064Z","creator":"Ada ","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>The music from the previous scene continues into the beginning of this one. While time has passed, the emotions and growing distance between Reynolds and Alma remain.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14724/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:34.683957679197235,46.84288507333033,293.0812692316306,199.38969852539572"}}},{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14724/canvas/1/ebd8a570-5554-4d38-8610-fb1fce3801a0","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-07-01T19:06:24.017Z","creator":"Ada ","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>In the press kit for the film, PTA describes Reynolds in no uncertain terms: “Dealing with Mr. Woodcock, however, is sometimes akin to battling fascist forces. He’s immensely talented, at the very top of his game, but he’s also fussy, self-consumed and difficult. . . . <strong>Phantom Thread</strong> is a variation on the gothic romance that examines the intimacy of falling in love against a backdrop of the dangerous battlefield known as the House of Woodcock” (Anderson, “A Brief Introduction by Paul Thomas Anderson,” 5). In this formulation of the plot, PTA highlights the film’s depiction of love as a battle that is ultimately resolved, if not ever fully stable, and its post-war setting’s influence.&nbsp;</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14724/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:754.812898089172,120.63744028662421,485.639928343949,561.9133160828025"}}}]}]}]}